# [s1 L1-L3] Paragraph
P: Plain paragraph summary text.

# [s2 L4-L7] Blockquote
Q: quoted line one quoted line two

# [s3 L8-L13] List
L: first item; second item; third item

# [s4 L14-L20] Code
C: rust, 3 lines

# [s5 L21-L26] Table
T: name | value (2 cols x 2 rows)

# [s6 L27-L28] Image
I: alt="diagram", src=path
